#: ../../source/chain/buzzer.rst:6 c0d989cf114349b79bb35d9c3549542a
msgid ""
"BuzzerChain is the helper class for buzzer devices on the Chain bus. It "
"provides methods to control buzzer frequency, duty cycle, play modes "
"(auto play, manual play, note play), and play musical notes."
msgstr ""
"BuzzerChain 是链式总线上蜂鸣器设备的辅助类。它提供了控制蜂鸣器频率、占空比、播放模式（自动播放、"
"手动播放、音符播放）以及播放音符的方法。"

