msgid ""
"This example demonstrates how to use the Chain Buzzer in auto play mode. "
"It initializes the buzzer RGB indicator, then plays 500 Hz, 1000 Hz, or "
"1500 Hz tones when button A, B, or C is clicked."
msgstr ""
"本示例演示如何在自动播放模式下使用 Chain Buzzer。它初始化蜂鸣器 RGB 指示灯，然后在按钮 A、B 或 C "
"被点击时播放 500 Hz、1000 Hz 或 1500 Hz 的音调。"

